description:
Merry Christmas from the Seventh-day Adventist Church! We hope you enjoy "God's Gifts," a festive international musical medley celebrating our many blessings. Wishing you a wonderful holiday season filled with joy, love and forgiveness, and a blessed New Year. 

The Seventh-day Adventist Church is a global Christian community of more than 17 million members living in 209 countries.

Help us caption & translate this video!
